OL,3,CManhunt after prisoner escapes from
OL,4,Cvan in Woolwich
OL,6,FPolice are hunting for a prisoner who
OL,7,Fescaped from a van in Woolwich.
OL,9,FTemitope Segun was last seen near
OL,10,FWoolwich High Street on Monday evening.
OL,12,FThe 25-year-old is believed to have
OL,13,Flinks to Plumstead, Abbey Wood and
OL,14,FWoolwich.
OL,16,FDetective Sergeant Claudine Manning,
OL,17,Fwho is leading the search, said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
