OL,3,CManhunt after prisoner escapes from
OL,4,Cvan in Woolwich
OL,6,F"My team of dedicated officers are
OL,7,Fworking around the clock to trace and
OL,8,Fapprehend Temitope Segun. It is
OL,9,Fimperative that the public contact
OL,10,Fpolice via 999 if they see him ` or
OL,11,Fknow where he may be.
OL,13,F"He was last seen wearing a black
OL,14,Fjacket, black trousers and black
OL,15,Ftrainers and has links across south
OL,16,FLondon."
OL,18,FPolice advise the public to not
OL,19,Fapproach Temitope Segun and instead
OL,20,Fdial 999, quoting 2270/10JUN.
